profile:
Based in Grimsby and serving the Niagara/Hamilton regions, Davies Home Improvements is owned and operated by Brian Davies, a carpenter and general contractor who specializes in home renovations. An experienced and skilled contractor, Brian believes in putting his customers first and has built his business by providing every customer with excellent service. 

Davies Home Improvements takes a customer-centric approach to contracting.
 
While Brian and his staff have the skill to complete your projects, they understand that when it comes to your home, you're the expert.
 
They work to provide their customers with a positive experience from start to finish.
 
Every project, big or small: 
Begins with a free consultation where they learn about your needs, starts on schedule and keeps to a time line that works for you, includes daily check-ins to keep you up-to-date and informed, ends as predicted: on time and budget.
